parameters.name: CertFile
parameters.description: Input stream for the portrait side of the ID card image. Choose either CertUrl or CertFile.

parameters.name: CertNationalFile
parameters.description: URL for the national emblem side of the ID card image. Choose either CertNationalUrl or CertNationalFile, or omit both.

parameters.name: CertNationalUrl
parameters.description: National emblem side of the ID card image URL. A publicly accessible HTTP or HTTPS link. You can choose either CertNationalUrl or CertNationalFile, or omit both.

parameters.name: CertUrl
parameters.description: Portrait side of the ID card image. A publicly accessible HTTP or HTTPS link. Choose either CertUrl or CertFile.
